{"tid":613733,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"金髮索女爆C朗裝假狗","createTime":"2018-04-02T02:55:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T06:42:21.000Z","uid":77132,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7ae55cf424334fdf168e08823ce7a84baf44a152","tid":613733,"uid":77132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T02:55:00.000Z","msg":"人紅招妒忌，入完歐戰100球嘅基斯坦奴朗拿度（C朗），啱啱先被小報爆料話背住女友暗撻天氣女郎，又有負面花邊新聞流出，就係之前曾自稱同佢有一腿嘅意大利名模Elisa De Panicis，上電視真人騷大爆呢位皇馬球星平時拍嗰啲露肉廣告，成日展示自己性感身材，其實唔係真材實料，而係做咗手腳。<br />\n<br />\nElisa特別指出，例如有時拍到C朗着底褲時「激凸」，其實係喺入面加咗墊，所以大家誤會以為佢好雄偉，根本就唔係嗰回事，仲話自己同C朗床上激戰過，只有佢最清楚。當然，C朗從來冇認過同Elisa有咩關係，信唔信呢個女人講，就閣下自行判斷啦！"},{"pid":"5b97c17631a53705d3edb7734c8ff9053a290d02","tid":613733,"uid":77132,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T02:55:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/105515_a792176865e1e0bf45e6db13a87c6381.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F105515_a792176865e1e0bf45e6db13a87c6381.png&h=3cf3bd38&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/105516_546c81a338896743814581420239c70c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F105516_546c81a338896743814581420239c70c.png&h=42f1af71&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/105516_8515ee520205bd0cc1b4f5c255dbed05.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F105516_8515ee520205bd0cc1b4f5c255dbed05.png&h=95271cd3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4dc131de79d4db941064da69967b3e9bf36e86ec","tid":613733,"uid":41963,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T02:56:59.000Z","msg":"c朗朴智星.gif"},{"pid":"bdf17736590772831285b8d5b2180c8e233d8c49","tid":613733,"uid":1265,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:16:10.000Z","msg"